Quickstrike:




Quickstrike looked and saw Dark Mouse's expression. He could almost 
feel her. He feared that she may do something foolish, so he snapped 
a large pincher at her nose. 

He eyed her a brief few seconds, then crawled out into better view of 
Megatron. He had do a little act. "What 'cha plannin' t' do, boss?" 
he asked Megatron.
